</div>
<div id="collapse6" class="collapse faqs-answer-collapse" aria-labelledby="heading6" data-parent="#accordion1">
<div class="card-body faqs-answer" style="padding-left: 20px;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">A living room can be made to look beautiful in multiple ways. Apart from decor, artwork, paintings and furnishings other elements like lighting fixtures, flooring, wall paint/ textures, ceiling design and furniture play an important role in beautifying a space. Also, how you place and arrange everything together makes all the difference too.</span></div>
